Description:
recv() function: receive (read) data from a connected socket.

Files:
lib/recv.c
lib/w32sock.h

Depends-on:
sys_socket
errno           [test "$ac_cv_header_winsock2_h" = yes]

configure.ac:
AC_REQUIRE([gl_HEADER_SYS_SOCKET])
if test "$ac_cv_header_winsock2_h" = yes; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([recv])
fi
gl_SYS_SOCKET_MODULE_INDICATOR([recv])

